{"tid":720500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國靚仔龍門趙賢祐零封德國當選全場最佳球員　聲言望到歐洲落班！","createTime":"2018-06-28T03:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T13:08:29.000Z","uid":49388,"like":56,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4cbd3a7ef014ed6c4b24a28039359f06450c0d","tid":720500,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"韓國雖然未能晉級，但分組賽最後一仗以2：0擊敗衛冕的德國，贏得不少掌聲。有「大邱迪基亞」之稱的門將趙賢祐，面對多名歐洲一線球星仍毫無懼色，全場作出6次撲救，力保清白之身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1589301/org/ec515c0ecb0655fc40e6be2c6831a833.JPG/Mz_FiFNVes5on4zUhiBBpSY2QGva3UImN-kZ7TfpGe0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1589301%2Forg%2Fec515c0ecb0655fc40e6be2c6831a833.JPG%2FMz_FiFNVes5on4zUhiBBpSY2QGva3UImN-kZ7TfpGe0&h=b2956446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙賢祐今屆世界盃表現一鳴驚人。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n正牌迪基亞踢完3場分組賽才錄得1次成功撲救，趙賢祐今場對德國，單場已做出6次撲救，僅比「墨西哥Sam哥」奧祖亞（9次撲救）與哥斯達黎加基羅拿華斯（7次撲救）的紀錄少。<br />\n<br />\n外表與韓國流行組合2AM前隊長趙權有幾分相似的趙賢祐，順理成章當選球迷心水最佳球員（Man of the Match）。不過，賽後出席記者會時，他保持一貫謙卑：「我整個職業生涯之中從未踢過這樣完美的一場比賽。今日我並非全靠自己的力量去救對手攻門──金承奎與金鎮鉉（兩名後備門將）都有幫助我。連同教練在內，整支韓國隊都是為韓國人民而戰。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1589302/org/f33d432ffdc0847331bb8d4076822cc3.JPG/0YHNyD0hn6mwRUXqewgkIlxuf-_5gfTucJ0M0XCdDNE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1589302%2Forg%2Ff33d432ffdc0847331bb8d4076822cc3.JPG%2F0YHNyD0hn6mwRUXqewgkIlxuf-_5gfTucJ0M0XCdDNE&h=7bdabb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一直不知道另一場F組比賽戰果的一班韓國球員，興奮慶祝打敗德國。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n完場才知出局<br />\n<br />\n他更透露，一直專心比賽，不知道原來球隊最終擊敗了德國也要出局：「完場後我們才知道另一場（瑞典3：0贏墨西哥）的戰果，我們感到很失望，所以很多人都哭了。」<br />\n<br />\n以闖英格蘭為目標<br />\n<br />\n身高1.89米、效力FC大邱的趙賢祐，本來並非韓國隊的正選門將，但這3場分組賽都擔正，以出色表現讓世人認識他，但他仍未敢自滿：「若然人們認為我踢得出色，我很高興。但這是團體運動，我要感謝隊友們與職員的支持。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，26歲的趙賢祐雄心壯志，目標未來衝出韓職：「希望我有一日能夠在歐洲聯賽比賽──最好是英格蘭。在那裏，你可以跟世上最頂級的射手交戰，不斷進步。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1589303/org/060a32bc2186166674163544f22ddbe1.jpg/-7zB2fFDnma0j3fBzsTSwIoneqGY4XzrN6R9qDekfag\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1589303%2Forg%2F060a32bc2186166674163544f22ddbe1.jpg%2F-7zB2fFDnma0j3fBzsTSwIoneqGY4XzrN6R9qDekfag&h=fc75113f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙賢祐今場作出多達6次撲救。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1589304/org/6a5be73832e5203be5477dce8d1b8046.jpg/__9gT6blYQAtPUnxHM8lPKGOdq0_QsrLACG4KwAhuCs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1589304%2Forg%2F6a5be73832e5203be5477dce8d1b8046.jpg%2F__9gT6blYQAtPUnxHM8lPKGOdq0_QsrLACG4KwAhuCs&h=6ba541df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前德甲神射手馬里奧高美斯今仗也無法射破趙賢祐大門。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1555791/org/25c915937181407e8d7906006601f70f.JPG/IibBS9QKXyfMPK-0hKU5K_LN8rK5K3wZIJWhZSCVoWU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1555791%2Forg%2F25c915937181407e8d7906006601f70f.JPG%2FIibBS9QKXyfMPK-0hKU5K_LN8rK5K3wZIJWhZSCVoWU&h=0c6b2b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1555794/org/4dafae319db1048040e1f5c9a10e9323.JPG/OyLVqsw56i4ACFSKfGMnGG8ctkuS_-XfVu7AGFbuwBg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1555794%2Forg%2F4dafae319db1048040e1f5c9a10e9323.JPG%2FOyLVqsw56i4ACFSKfGMnGG8ctkuS_-XfVu7AGFbuwBg&h=4b5a955f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1589320/org/f66ad55c507e3287339194f931d3e4f7.jpg/_Ph_BTunCy4oEZGZ0X9On0rzzACwsaQ5i4_iBYuP4gU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1589320%2Forg%2Ff66ad55c507e3287339194f931d3e4f7.jpg%2F_Ph_BTunCy4oEZGZ0X9On0rzzACwsaQ5i4_iBYuP4gU&h=fbe7df6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1589330/org/45345d5da11b2a53a9184933f3da337c.jpg/dGfuUHBUS8M7bOViSwwBlH9MwQIr8HV-KfNqPynzaj8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1589330%2Forg%2F45345d5da11b2a53a9184933f3da337c.jpg%2FdGfuUHBUS8M7bOViSwwBlH9MwQIr8HV-KfNqPynzaj8&h=769a1369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙賢祐外表有幾分像2AM前隊長趙權。（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"ede04b14ea26a6b44588f8098239a5141f5e8e3d","tid":720500,"uid":6577,"like":315,"dislike":8,"score":307,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:21:12.000Z","msg":"靚仔？ 成個笑波子咁撚樣"},{"pid":"fe23a585e90bdec16572a4e63f08647d08e2fa88","tid":720500,"uid":17088,"like":32,"dislike":5,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:22:31.000Z","msg":"琴晚係打得幾好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/south_korea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea197d49668ea6683fd94f8ac7dc7a12749d85a","tid":720500,"uid":17669,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"係嘅，意西德都唔歡迎韓狗，惟有望去英"},{"pid":"a2a39461005623c1d20beb3f108d9ad289f98c04","tid":720500,"uid":22141,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:23:34.000Z","msg":"雖然佢化妝 但呢三場真係打得唔錯"},{"pid":"3c9be2aff2a95d3f950747fff9abea9190ac086b","tid":720500,"uid":135380,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係踢波要搽防曬 咁撚白既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7207769fedc0b0d4b9712ca6508c1c910e160459","tid":720500,"uid":42182,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"靚仔就唔係架啦<br />\n不過佢算係外表睇落去比較斯文，唔似打籠"},{"pid":"cc8dbcb95c501c621dfcefa205670a634c638205","tid":720500,"uid":62343,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"去利記啦"},{"pid":"b29402cba624a8eee28301a0a2f1d29a3aee0665","tid":720500,"uid":42820,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"唔免兵役搵鬼要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186e068b68d142b41387df287cf5b7a091b75bf6","tid":720500,"uid":42182,"like":163,"dislike":3,"score":160,"quote":{"pid":"3c9be2aff2a95d3f950747fff9abea9190ac086b","tid":720500,"uid":135380,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係踢波要搽防曬 咁撚白既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/112704_c72a35d22b6cb09728dd8728ffd99c6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F112704_c72a35d22b6cb09728dd8728ffd99c6a.png&h=9b97800a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a71cea3e708aaac7a99da747b3d1665d5e7904c1","tid":720500,"uid":149607,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"個樣似道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02af95afd32ba40cb0d5e7eeeb2f6a45f9d691e","tid":720500,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"靚仔定義真廣"},{"pid":"aea7dfcc26b9c9f2d00bbcde2e0147f1801d5520","tid":720500,"uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"韓國「美白」門將趙賢祐膺全場最佳 稱「球員生涯從沒踢過比這場更好的表現」 (01:55)<br />\n<br />\n今屆世界盃因臉色蒼白而成為話題的韓國門將趙賢祐，昨仗踢出身價助球隊爆大冷擊敗德國。賽後獲選為全場最佳球員的他，坦言自己球員生涯「從沒踢過比這場更好的表現」。<br />\n<br />\n今屆賽事因外型而成為外界焦點的韓國「美白」門將趙賢祐，是役助球隊爆冷以2：0擊敗德國表現出色，多次化解德國隊攻門的他，賽後更獲選為全場最佳球員。賽後他說坦言：「老實說，我球員生涯從沒踢過比這場更好的表現，不論是國家隊或球會。出局是令人失望的，但這場我們為了國民而戰踢出了漂亮一仗。」<br />\n<br />\n至於韓國教練申台龍則大讚麾下：「賽前我向球員們說，即使贏的機會哪怕只有百分之一，只要拚到最後便什麼都有可能發生。」"},{"pid":"1b2e0d4b5e93824ba6dae892ea78df4df8abb3e1","tid":720500,"uid":94739,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"要當兵 搵鬼買你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707da79b1803f8fc6dccad91d53e778d130319c5","tid":720500,"uid":42152,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"rep